This paper is primarily focused on image understanding and captioning, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also introduces a novel architecture that integrates hierarchical structure into image encoding, which could be of interest to researchers in machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
